reviewText: I've known Sam for over forty years. As someone who helped him shoot some of this footage, I've seen Sam's highs and lows and his life closely mirrors a lot of ours. I admire the fact he swallows his pride and isn't afraid to show himself as he really is. He went viral before viral existed.

Romance, tragedy, desire, shame, lust, gluttony, hope, love, life, reality all rolled into one, a culmination of the human experience lived through the eyes of an optimist who hits reality at 120mph...and lives to tell the tale! highly entertaining and well crafted. A must watch!
